  "content_markdown": "Version: 8.2Bank Customer JourneyLendingBank Sales\nOn this page\nUse the **Product categories and types** lookup to form bank product categories and types, as well as add [document packages](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2156#title-2924-8) to generate automatically in the product sales conditions. The lookup also contains [criteria](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2156#title-2924-17) by which a manager can modify the product sales conditions.\nThe product category in the **Product categories and types** lookup includes several product types (Fig. 1).\nFig. 1 The structure of the [Product categories and types] lookup\n![Fig. 1 The structure of the \\[Product categories and types\\] lookup](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/en/files/2020-11/section_lookups_categories_and_types.png)\n## Create a product category\u200b\nTo add a product category to a lookup:\n1. Click ![](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/default/files/inline-images/system_designer.png) to open the System Designer.\n2. Click the **Lookups** link in the **System setup** block.\n3. Open the **Product categories and types** lookup. \n4. Click the **New category** button (Fig. 2).\nFig. 2 Adding a product category to the [Product categories and types] lookup\n![Fig. 2 Adding a product category to the \\[Product categories and types\\] lookup](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/en/files/2020-11/section_lookups_new_category.png)\n5. Enter the product category name (for example, \"Loan\") and select the class (for example, \"Product\") (Fig. 3).\nFig. 3 Example of adding a new product category\n![Fig. 3 Example of adding a new product category](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/en/files/2020-11/section_lookups_create_category.png)\n6. Click **Save**.\n7. Add other product categories to the lookup in the same manner.\n## Add product category\u200b\nTo add products to a category:\n1. Select the needed category in the area on the right side of the lookup page and click the ![](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/default/files/inline-images/btn_com_menu_gear_1.png) button.\n2. Select the **New type** command (Fig. 4).\nFig. 4 Adding a new product type to a category\n![Fig. 4 Adding a new product type to a category](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/en/files/2020-11/section_lookups_new_type.png)\n3. Enter the product type name (for example, \"Consumer lending\").\n4. Save the changes.\n5. Add other product types of this category in the same manner.\n* * *\n## See also\u200b\n[Create a card](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1076)\n[Create a financial account](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=1078)\n[Form product conditions](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2156)\n[Copy a product with conditions](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?id=2157)",
